flowchart TD
  S01[01 Scan / Snapshot] --> S02[02 Analysis / Classification]
  S02 --> S0225[02.25 Recalibration / Finding Refinement]
  S0225 --> H[Handoff Statement]
  H --> P[02.5 Pre-Simulation Package]
  P --> Q{Admission conditions satisfied?}
  Q -- Yes --> S03[03 Simulation Environment]
  Q -- Missing declared dependency --> D{Auto-Dependency?}
  D -- ON --> LP[Local in-scope preparation only]
  D -- OFF --> RU[Request participant action]
  LP --> P
  RU --> P
  Q -- Isolation reason --> I[Isolation Add-On]
  Q -- Reattempt --> P
  S03 --> S04[04 Replay / Proof]
  S04 --> S05{05 User Apply or Cancel}
  S05 -- Cancel --> S08[08 Final Result Locked]
  S05 -- Apply --> S06[06 Explicit User Apply Mutation Relay]
  S06 --> S07[07 Post-Apply Verification]
  S07 --> S08
